PIXART IMAGING I said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 36.09% to NT$255,215,000 from NT$399,340,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            255,215          399,340    
YOY%             -36.09%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,501,100        2,264,394   
YOY%             -33.71% 
